## SECTION 1: EXECUTIVE SUMMARY

### 1.1 Business Overview

Burger Empire (operated by A1 Foods) is a multi-outlet budget Quick Service Restaurant (QSR) chain headquartered in Gwalior, Madhya Pradesh. Founded in 2018 by **Animesh Gupta and Rahul Saraogi** (from Jhansi, UP), the brand pioneered affordable burgers, wraps, and fast food for Gwalior's student and youth demographic. It operates 6–8 outlets across Gwalior and a national network of 19+ outlets in 15+ cities, making it the leading homegrown burger chain in central India.

The brand was formally incubated at the **RISE Jhansi Incubation Centre Foundation** (Jhansi Smart City Limited), and won the inaugural *"Startup of the Month"* award. It operates a **FOFO (Franchise Owned, Franchise Operated)** model with active franchise listings on FranchiseBazar and IID.

